{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1733761154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We designed Harvest Village to be the best city building game. We want it to appeal to everyone and become a timeless classic, so we didn't limit it to a specific theme, such as medieval city building game or ancient city building game. In this city, you also need to collect resources, process them, complete various quests, and try to craft the most valuable items. In other words, unlike the crafting games you are used to, everything you produce will contribute to the development of both your city and yourself. Upgrade your buildings and become the best miner, cook and toolmaker - anything is possible in this infinite crafting game! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">32 Pieces Of Armor You Can Craft.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/extras/ArmorGif.gif?t=1733761154\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40 Pieces Of Melee Weapon You Can Craft.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/extras/WeaponGif.gif?t=1733761154\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">24 Pieces Of Ranged Weapon You Can Craft. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/extras/RangedG\u0130f.gif?t=1733761154\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">9 Pieces Of Vegetable You Can Grow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 Types Of Minerals You Can Collect.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8 Types Of Bush And Berries You Can Collect.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/extras/Material.gif?t=1733761154\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">21 Types Of Food You Can Cook.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/extras/FoodGif.gif?t=1733761154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">9 Pieces Of Tool You Can Craft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 Accessible and Upgradable Buildings. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More than 135 Tasks To Complete.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733761154","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733761154","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/417698302bd6b266e6fd7f7a60548531215f04e5/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733761154","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/417698302bd6b266e6fd7f7a60548531215f04e5/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733761154","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210720/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1733761154\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We designed Harvest Village to be the best city building game. We want it to appeal to everyone and become a timeless classic, so we didn't limit it to a specific theme, such as medieval city building game or ancient city building game. In this city, you also need to collect resources, process them, complete various quests, and try to craft the most valuable items. In other words, unlike the crafting games you are used to, everything you